name: Belkin F7D2102 802.11a/b/g/n USB Type-A Wi-Fi Adapter
Features: [Compact Design, Backward-compatible with 802.11a/g devices at 54 Mbps and 802.11b products at 11 Mbps, the N300 Micro Wireless USB Adapter can connect to older wireless networks and hotspots as well as newer 802.11n networks and wireless-N devices that offer increased range and speed.]
